    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: National Collaborating Centre for Nursing and Supportive Care. Violence: the short-term management of disturbed/violent behaviour in psychiatric in-patient settings and emergency departments. London (UK): National Institute for Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2005 Feb. 292 p.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
